    "vignette": "A 28-year-old woman comes to her psychiatrist for a renewal of her prescription for haloperidol. She has been on this drug for 6 months after she was hospitalized for a psychotic episode. She complains to the psychiatrist about a white milky discharge from both of her breasts. What is the mechanism of action which 1s causing this medication-induced effect?",
