    "source": "pretest",
    "difficulty": 2,
    "vignette": "A 44-year-old man has had a traumatic injury to his brain. Since the accident, he has appeared inattentive and under-motivated. He tends to linger on trivial thoughts and echoes the examiner’s questions. Which area of the man’s brain 1s likely to have been traumatized?",
