    "vignette": "A diagnostic test 1s found to have the following characteristics: Number Number Total of patients of patients number of with the without the patients illness illness Presence of Substance 33 50 83 X in the blood Absence of Substance 5 37 4? Xin the blood Total 38 87 125 Which of the following formulas will allow you to correctly calculate the sensitivity of this diagnostic test? a. b. C. d. 38/125 = 0.30 33/83 = 0.40 37/87 = 0.43 83/125 = 0.66",
