    "id": "PT-EVAL-033",
    "domain": "evaluation",
    "source": "pretest",
    "difficulty": 2,
    "vignette": "A 56-year-old man is brought to the physician’s office by his wife because she has noted a personality change during the past 3 months. While the patient is being interviewed, he answers every question with the same three words. Which of the following symptoms best fits this patient’s behavior?",
    "question": "Select the best answer.",
