    "id": "PT-EVAL-036",
    "domain": "evaluation",
    "source": "pretest",
    "difficulty": 2,
    "vignette": "A 26-year-old woman with panic disorder notes that during the middle of one of her attacks she feels as if she is disconnected from her body, and feels as if she is floating above it. Which of the following terms best describes this symptom?",
